<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Linux - Category - Web Developer Hodory</title><link>http://blog.hodory.dev/categories/linux/</link><description>Linux - Category - Web Developer Hodory</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>ko</language><managingEditor>master@hodory.dev (hodory)</managingEditor><webMaster>master@hodory.dev (hodory)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sat, 21 Nov 2020 23:42:03 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://blog.hodory.dev/categories/linux/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SSL Connection Error 발생</title><link>http://blog.hodory.dev/2020/11/21/ssl-connection-error/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Nov 2020 23:42:03 +0000</pubDate><author><name>hodory</name></author><guid>http://blog.hodory.dev/2020/11/21/ssl-connection-error/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">root</span><span class="nv">@aaaaa</span> <span class="p">~]</span><span class="c"># curl -XGET {{링크}}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">curl</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">35</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">SSL</span> <span class="n">connect</span> <span class="n">error</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="원인" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%ec%9b%90%ec%9d%b8" class="header-mark"></a>원인</h3><hr>
<p>Curl 버전이 낮아서 발생하는 문제</p>
<h2 id="해결방법" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%ed%95%b4%ea%b2%b0%eb%b0%a9%eb%b2%95" class="header-mark"></a>해결방법</h2><hr>
<h3 id="패키지를-업데이트-할-수-있을-때" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%ed%8c%a8%ed%82%a4%ec%a7%80%eb%a5%bc-%ec%97%85%eb%8d%b0%ec%9d%b4%ed%8a%b8-%ed%95%a0-%ec%88%98-%ec%9e%88%ec%9d%84-%eb%95%8c" class="header-mark"></a>패키지를 업데이트 할 수 있을 때</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">$</span> <span class="n">yum</span> <span class="n">update</span> <span class="n">-y</span> <span class="n">nss</span> <span class="nb">curl </span><span class="n">libcurl</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="패키지를-업데이트-할-수-없을-때" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%ed%8c%a8%ed%82%a4%ec%a7%80%eb%a5%bc-%ec%97%85%eb%8d%b0%ec%9d%b4%ed%8a%b8-%ed%95%a0-%ec%88%98-%ec%97%86%ec%9d%84-%eb%95%8c" class="header-mark"></a>패키지를 업데이트 할 수 없을 때</h3><p><code>-1</code> 을 파라미터로 넣어주면 해결 가능하다. (<a href="https://github.com/userify/shim/issues/25" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/userify/shim/issues/25</a>)</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">$</span> <span class="nb">curl </span><span class="n">-XGET</span> <span class="p">{{</span><span class="err">링크</span><span class="p">}}</span> <span class="n">-k</span> <span class="mf">-1</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="참고-자료" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%ec%b0%b8%ea%b3%a0-%ec%9e%90%eb%a3%8c" class="header-mark"></a>참고 자료</h2><hr>
